{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|26}} There thou shalt offer thy burnt offerings, and there thou shalt do all that I command thee.

{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|27}} Notwithstanding thou mayest kill and eat flesh in all thy gates, whatsoever thy soul lusteth after,

