{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|46}} And thou shalt offer thy burnt offerings, the flesh and the blood, upon the altar of the LORD thy God:

{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|47}} And the blood of thy sacrifices shall be poured out upon the altar of the LORD thy God, and thou shalt eat the flesh.

{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|48}} Observe and hear all these words which I command thee, that it may go well with thee, and with thy children after thee for ever,

