{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|28}} Three times in a year shall all thy males appear before the LORD thy God in the place which he shall choose;

{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|29}} In the feast of unleavened bread, and in the feast of weeks, and in the feast of tabernacles:

{{font|size=smaller|color=#0000FF|30}} And they shall not appear before the LORD empty: every man shall give as he is able,

